summary: Friendly reminder that moomin and snufkin are not children or teenagers. They are technically ageless, but if you really had to...
body:
Friendly reminder that moomin and snufkin are not children or teenagers. They are technically ageless, but if you really had to pin some age on them they are young adults

Just because they appeared on shows aimed for children doesn’t mean they ARE children themselves.
